list.name: Default
list.comment: Loggable was reading a file each time it was instantiated. Very inefficient. Now reading file once and requesting N number of lines from it at start of execution.

task.summary: Added PieceLIbrary, added more GUI elements to PieceBuilderSlate
Fixed empty overwriting issue. Now can save editted pieces and load them properly.
Fixed: Changing name of piece resulted in incorrect file output.
Massive overhaul of moving mechanics. Cleaned up code considerably. Board updates pieces' move locations instead of pieces asking board where they can go.
Cleaned up Timer. Now sleeps for 1 second instead of polling.
Cleaned up Timer implementation in GameMode. Also, stops timer on game end.
Cleaned up MoveStyle: no longer extends Loggable. toString does something useful now.
Fixed creating two MainMenuSlates in Runner instead of one.
Loggable was reading a file each time it was instantiated. Very inefficient. Now reading file once and requesting N number of lines from it at start of execution.
